    "official_link":  null,
    "org_about":  "The German University in Cairo (GUC) was established in 2002 in cooperation with several German universities and academic institutions, with the goal of delivering internationally recognized education in Egypt. It offers a wide range of programs in engineering, pharmacy, management, applied sciences, and arts, among others. GUC is known for its modern curricula, hands-on approach to teaching, and a multicultural academic environment that fosters innovation and research.",
    "en":  {
               "lang":  "en",
               "title":  "Fully Funded Scholarship at the German University in Cairo",
               "sections":  [
                                {
                                    "header":  "Opportunity description",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"description\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"255\" data-start=\"64\"\u003eSince its establishment, the German University in Cairo (GUC) has adopted a policy that supports academically outstanding students by providing various and well-balanced scholarship programs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"520\" data-start=\"257\"\u003eGUC\u0026rsquo;s mission is founded on attracting creative, academically active high school graduates and supporting them through an educational environment that fosters their abilities and skills in both teaching and research, as well as enhancing their personal potential.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"547\" data-start=\"527\"\u003eMain Scholarships\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"580\" data-start=\"549\"\u003e1. New Student Scholarships\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"740\" data-start=\"581\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"665\" data-start=\"581\"\u003eFull or partial scholarships for top high school graduates or their equivalents.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"740\" data-start=\"666\"\u003eTuition fee exemption, provided a minimum GPA of 3.00 (C) is maintained.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"778\" data-start=\"742\"\u003e2. Enrolled Student Scholarships\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"954\" data-start=\"779\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"840\" data-start=\"779\"\u003eAwarded to current students with outstanding performance.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"954\" data-start=\"841\"\u003eThe program also offers sports scholarships for those with exceptional achievements at the international level.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"999\" data-start=\"956\"\u003e3. Scholarship for High School Students\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"1204\" data-start=\"1000\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1091\" data-start=\"1000\"\u003eOffered to students who rank among the top 10 in the national high school examinations.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1204\" data-start=\"1092\"\u003eCovers tuition fees, accommodation for non-residents (if available), transportation, test fees, and insurance.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1261\" data-start=\"1206\"\u003e4. Scholarships for Holders of Foreign Certificates\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"1494\" data-start=\"1262\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1377\" data-start=\"1262\"\u003eFull or partial scholarships for holders of Abitur, IGCSE, American Diploma, and other equivalent certificates.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1494\" data-start=\"1378\"\u003eRequires passing GUC admission tests and adhering to the university\u0026rsquo;s regulations, with a minimum GPA of 3.00 (C).\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1525\" data-start=\"1496\"\u003e5. Nile Basin Scholarship\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"1749\" data-start=\"1526\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1638\" data-start=\"1526\"\u003eOffered in cooperation with the Egyptian Ministry of Foreign Affairs for students from Nile Basin countries.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1749\" data-start=\"1639\"\u003eRequires passing GUC admission tests and providing an official endorsement letter from the relevant embassy.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 data-end=\"1809\" data-start=\"1751\"\u003e6. Scholarship for Students from Egyptian Governorates\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"2026\" data-start=\"1810\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"1896\" data-start=\"1810\"\u003eAllocates 54 full scholarships to top high school students across 27 governorates.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2026\" data-start=\"1897\"\u003eCovers tuition fees, accommodation (subject to availability), transportation, test fees, and insurance.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"2026\" data-start=\"2026\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"2026\" data-start=\"2026\"\u003eDeadlines\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"2545\" data-start=\"2026\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2171\" data-start=\"2026\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"2052\" data-start=\"2026\"\u003eHigh School Certificate\u003c/strong\u003e: Final date for scholarship consideration is August 21, and financial aid applications are accepted until August 23.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2282\" data-start=\"2172\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"2190\" data-start=\"2174\"\u003eAbitur \u0026amp; FOS\u003c/strong\u003e: July 15 (deadline for scholarships and financial aid); refunds available until August 5.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2431\" data-start=\"2283\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"2340\" data-start=\"2285\"\u003eAmerican Diploma \u0026amp; Other International Certificates\u003c/strong\u003e: July 18 (deadline for scholarships and financial aid); refunds available until July 29.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2545\" data-start=\"2432\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"2450\" data-start=\"2434\"\u003eIGCSE \u0026amp; GCSE\u003c/strong\u003e: August 19 (deadline for scholarships and financial aid); refunds available until September 2.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"2575\" data-start=\"2552\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"2575\" data-start=\"2552\"\u003eFinancial Aid Policy\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"2884\" data-start=\"2577\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2750\" data-start=\"2577\"\u003eFinancial aid is granted to students who face financial difficulties, those who have siblings studying at GUC, or those with outstanding sports or cultural achievements.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"2884\" data-start=\"2751\"\u003eAid continues throughout the study period as long as the student maintains a GPA of 3.00 (C) and adheres to university regulations.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"2912\" data-start=\"2891\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"2912\" data-start=\"2891\"\u003eRegistration Steps\u003c/h2\u003e\u003col data-end=\"3371\" data-start=\"2914\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3003\" data-start=\"2914\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"2939\" data-start=\"2917\"\u003eOnline Application\u003c/strong\u003e: Complete the online form to receive your application number.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3121\" data-start=\"3004\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"3037\" data-start=\"3007\"\u003eBooking the Admission Test\u003c/strong\u003e: You will receive an email from the Admissions Office to schedule your test date.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3243\" data-start=\"3122\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"3140\" data-start=\"3125\"\u003eOn Test Day\u003c/strong\u003e: Arrive early with your ID card, the test fee (EGP 650, non-refundable), and any required documents.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3371\" data-start=\"3244\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"3293\" data-start=\"3247\"\u003eFor Applied Arts and Architecture Students\u003c/strong\u003e: Submit a portfolio and pass both the aptitude test and a personal interview.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"3395\" data-start=\"3378\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ch2 data-end=\"3395\" data-start=\"3378\"\u003eAdmission Test\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul data-end=\"3689\" data-start=\"3397\"\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3497\" data-start=\"3397\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"3430\" data-start=\"3399\"\u003eReasoning Test (50 minutes)\u003c/strong\u003e: Assesses comprehension, verbal relations, and inference skills.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3616\" data-start=\"3498\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"3538\" data-start=\"3500\"\u003eEnglish Language Test (45 minutes)\u003c/strong\u003e: Covers language usage, reading comprehension, and listening comprehension.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-end=\"3689\" data-start=\"3617\"\u003eIf a student fails, they may retake the test once more free of charge.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"3812\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"3696\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-end=\"3812\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-start=\"3696\"\u003eFor more information and details, please visit the official GUC website or contact the Admissions Office. Good luck!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
                                },
                                {
                                    "header":  "Benefits",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"benefits\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
                                },
                                {
                                    "header":  "Eligibility criteria",
                                    "body":  "\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"qualifications\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"
                                }
                            ]
